### List all users (admin only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### List guides only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users?role=GUIDE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get a specific user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update a user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "stationId": "{{stationId}}"
}

###

### Suspend a user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "SUSPENDED"
}

###

### Reactivate a user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

### Create a new admin account (admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/admins
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "Admin",
  "email": "newadmin@sfcpark.com"
}
